Title: The Socratic Method
Plot: Dr. House is intrigued by the symptoms of a schizophrenic woman, who displays mixed symptoms, including a tumor, but soon realizes the source of her problems isn't the obvious. House confronts his birthday and Chase confronts his past when the mother's son tries to keep up with her condition.
GuestStars: Stacy Edwards, Aaron Himelstein, John Prosky, Sonya Eddy, Pat Musick, Lilas Lane, Veronica Leigh, C. Xavier Drayton
